{"questionId":"9522","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Consider the system of paired differential equations</p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\dot x = 3x + 2y\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mover>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>˙</mo>\n    </mover>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\dot y = 2x + 3y\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mover>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n      <mo>˙</mo>\n    </mover>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n</math></span>.</p>\n<p>This represents the populations of two species of symbiotic toadstools in a large wood.</p>\n<p>Time <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"t\">\n  <mi>t</mi>\n</math></span> is measured in decades.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Given the initial conditions that when&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"t = 0\">\n  <mi>t</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x = 150\">\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>150</mn>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y = 50\">\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>50</mn>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;find the particular solution.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>Require <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"A + B = 150,{\\text{ }} - A + B = 50 \\Rightarrow A = 50,{\\text{ B = 100}}\">\n  <mi>A</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>B</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>150</mn>\n  <mo>,</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>A</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>B</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>50</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>A</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>50</mn>\n  <mo>,</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;B = 100</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>Particular solution is&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  x \\\\   y  \\end{array}} \\right) = 50{e^t}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right) + 100{e^{5t}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   1  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>y</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>50</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mi>t</mi>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>100</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>5</mn>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9522","referenceCode":"EXM.2.AHL.TZ0.1b.i","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Given the initial conditions that when t = 0 , x = 150 , y = 50 , find the particular solution.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5—Calculus","Topic 5—Calculus","AHL 5.17—Phase portrait"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}